---
layout: base.njk
title: Precision. Balance. Control.
description: Expert sidemount scuba diving training and gear reviews from a RAID Tech Trimix Sidemount Instructor.
---

<section class="hero" aria-label="Hero">
  <div class="hero-bg-image">
    <img
      src="/images/logo-hero.webp"
      alt="Sidemount Authority — Precision. Balance. Control."
      class="hero-full-img"
      loading="eager"
    />
    <div class="hero-full-overlay"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-hud-overlay" role="region" aria-label="Dive computer readouts">
    <div class="hud-overlay-cell">
      <span class="hud-bar-label">LAT</span>
      <span class="hud-bar-sep">—</span>
      <span class="hud-bar-value">24.5551° N</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hud-overlay-cell">
      <span class="hud-bar-label">DEPTH</span>
      <span class="hud-bar-sep">—</span>
      <span class="hud-bar-value">55.4 M</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hud-overlay-cell">
      <span class="hud-bar-label">SAC</span>
      <span class="hud-bar-sep">—</span>
      <span class="hud-bar-value">16 L/MIN</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hud-overlay-cell">
      <span class="hud-bar-label">TRIM</span>
      <span class="hud-bar-sep">—</span>
      <span class="hud-bar-value">LOCKED</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-body">
    <p class="hero-subtitle">Instructor-led sidemount diving training, gear reviews, and field-tested technique. No fluff. No affiliate hype. Just what works underwater.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta-bar">
      <a href="/training/" class="btn btn-signal">Start Training</a>
      <a href="/gear-tips/" class="btn btn-ghost">Browse Gear Tips</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>


<section class="photo-band" aria-label="Featured image">
  <img src="/images/diver-eyecontact.webp" alt="Technical sidemount diver making eye contact in dark open water" class="photo-band-img" loading="lazy" />
  <div class="photo-band-overlay">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="photo-band-text">
        <span class="eyebrow">Sidemount Diving, Done Right</span>
       <p class="photo-band-quote">Precision.<br>Balance.<br><span class="control">Control.</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<section class="pillars" aria-labelledby="pillars-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">The Foundation</span>
      <h2 id="pillars-heading">Built for Technical Divers</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="pillars-grid">
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">⊕</div>
        <h3>Training &amp; Certification</h3>
        <p>What sidemount certification involves, how to choose the right course, and how to prep so your check-out dives go smoothly.</p>
        <a href="/training/" class="read-more">Explore Training →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">◈</div>
        <h3>Gear Tips &amp; Reviews</h3>
        <p>Harnesses, cylinders, regulators, and fins — tested in the water, compared honestly, with real trim and balance notes.</p>
        <a href="/gear-tips/" class="read-more">Browse Tips →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">◎</div>
        <h3>Technique &amp; Community</h3>
        <p>Trim, valve drills, gas management, and the small adjustments that separate a comfortable sidemount diver from a struggling one.</p>
        <a href="/about/" class="read-more">Meet the Authority →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


{% set recentPosts = collections.posts | reverse | slice(0, 3) %}
{% if recentPosts.length %}
<section class="featured-tips" aria-labelledby="tips-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">Field-tested insight</span>
      <h2 id="tips-heading">Latest From the Field</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="featured-tips-grid">
      {% for post in recentPosts %}
      <article class="post-card">
        {% if post.data.hero_image %}
        <div class="post-card-image">
          <img src="{{ post.data.hero_image }}" alt="{{ post.data.hero_image_alt or post.data.title }}" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="post-card-body">
          <div class="post-card-meta">
            <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | postDate }}</time>
            {% if post.data.readTime %}<span>{{ post.data.readTime }} min</span>{% endif %}
          </div>
          <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
          {% if post.data.description %}<p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="post-card-footer">
          <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:center; margin-top:3rem;">
      <a href="/gear-tips/" class="btn btn-ghost">All Gear Tips →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}


<section class="cta-band" aria-labelledby="cta-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 id="cta-heading">Ready to dive with control?</h2>
    <p>Whether you're considering your first sidemount course or refining trim after years in the configuration — start here.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/training/" class="btn btn-signal">Find Your Course</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-ghost">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
